Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，吵醒你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在大掃除
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在曬榻榻米
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大掃除啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.61,0:03:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們經常受您的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公寓裡大掃除的工作\N不也需要男人幫忙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
