Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.15,0:03:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.15,0:03:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻煩你了
